ActWitness Protection Program Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Schedule to the Witness Protection Program Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE WITNESS PROTECTION PROGRAM ACT in order to facilitate timely access to federal documents (e.g., passports, social insurance numbers, status cards, etc.) that are required for a secure identity change to better protect witnesses admitted into Saskatchewan's witness protection program.
